&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">原因：rvm 版本bug
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">解决方法：
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">命令查看：
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> 正常：
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> [root@server002 ~]# trap
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> trap -- &amp;#39;&amp;#39; SIGTSTP
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> trap -- &amp;#39;&amp;#39; SIGTTIN
